  "summary": "sviehb/jefferson vulnerable to path traversal",
  "details": "A vulnerability has been found in the sviehb/jefferson JFFS2 filesystem extraction tool. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the file `src/scripts/jefferson`. The manipulation leads to path traversal. The attack can be initiated remotely. Upgrading to version 0.4 is able to address this issue as it includes https://github.com/sviehb/jefferson/commit/53b3f2fc34af0bb32afbcee29d18213e61471d87.",
